TomGine Render Engine - Image Processing

OpenGL Rendering engine - addon for GPU shader programms

Modules:
    - GPU image processing: Add, Dilate, Gauss, Invert, Multiply, Param2Polar, RGB2HSV, Sobel, Spreading, Thinning, Thresholding, NURBS curve, NURBS surfaces, NURBS volumes, texturing
    - Histogram descriptor (gradient + colour)

Requirements
	rt		(real-time clock)
	freeglut3-dev
	libftgl2, libftgl-dev (render text in OpenGL)
	libhighgui-dev (opencv - image file loading/saving)
    TomGine
	
Keyboard mapping:
	[Escape]: Close programme
	[w]: Toggle wireframe mode
	[Keypad_0, z]:	Reset to initial camera view
	
Mouse mapping:
	[Left Mouse Button + Move]: Rotate view about COR (Center of Rotation)
	[Right Mouse Button + Move]: Translate view
	[Mouse Wheel]: Zoom in/out

